M||tx|When the us wants to cr, plan, or op a lead magnet for em capture or lead generation. Also use when the us mentions "lead magnet," "gated cn," "cn upgrade," "downloadable," "ebook," "cheat sheet," "checklist," "template download," "opt-in," "freebie," "PDF download," "resource library," "cn offer," "em capture cn," "Notion template," "spreadsheet template," or "what shd I give away for emails." Use this for planning what to cr and how to distribute it. For interactive tools as lead magnets, see free-tool-st. For writing the actual cn, see copywriting. For the em sequence after capture, see em-sequence.
