M|Gati|tx|\| Approach \| When to Use \| Trade-off \|
M|Gati|tx|\|----------\|-------------\|-----------\|
M|Gati|tx|\| **Full gate** \| hi-value cn, bottom-funnel \| Max capture, lower reach \|
